item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】FLAC - Various Artists - Crossroads: More Music from the Major Motion Picture (Fan Made)
item.description:
​

Crossroads: More Music from the Major Motion Picture is a compilation of songs featured in the 2002 movie Crossroads starring Britney Spears, Zoe Saldana, Taryn Manning, and Anson Mount.

The set is made up of several songs that were not released on either of the official Crossroads soundtracks: 2002's Crossroads: Music from the Major Motion Picture and 2023's Crossroads: Special Edition - with the sole exception being Bowling for Soup's "Greatest Day," which was included on the 2002 soundtrack.

Interestingly, the Special Edition of the album omits "Greatest Day" and also features the original version of "How I Could Just Kill A Man" by Cypress Hill, while the movie features the popular cover by Rage Against the Machine.

(These tracks were collected from several sources around the web. Please be mindful and kind prior to downloading - I'm sharing this because I love music and I'm a bit of a completionist.)

1. Britney Spears - I Love Rock 'N Roll
2. Madonna - Open Your Heart
3. *NSYNC - Bye Bye Bye
4. Mystikal feat. Pharrell - Shake Ya Ass (Radio Edit)
5. Boomkat - Crazylove
6. Bowling for Soup - Greatest Day
7. Rage Against the Machine - How I Could Just Kill A Man
8. Lit - Lipstick and Bruises
9. New Birth Brass Band - Spread Your Legs
10. Travis - Follow the Light
11. Bowling for Soup - You and Me
12. Britney Spears - Overprotected (Album Version)
